line_1: See! crowded beds in those contiguous rooms;
line_2: Yet, ere they go, a greater evil comes —
How vainly spread with Carpets and Perfumes:

line_2: Descend to gamesters, prostitutes, and grooms.

line_2: Midst pois'nous smokes and steams, and rattling looms;

line_2: See with Joy my ROMEO comes;
